summary: This document is a certification from the Secretary of State of Delaware confirming that Hyperionair, Inc. is duly incorporated and in good standing as of September 23, 2013. It states that the annual reports and franchise taxes have been filed and paid to date.
keyFacts: Hyperionair, Inc. is incorporated in Delaware.
The company is in good standing as of September 23, 2013.
Annual reports have been filed to date.
Franchise taxes have been paid to date.
